{
  "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "这是一片数学画出来的雪花，边缘越看越细，怎么放大都有花边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "它有个古怪的名字，叫科赫雪花，藏着一个让人吃惊的秘密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "别急，我们从一个普通的等边三角形开始，一步步把它变成雪花。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-1",
      "filename": "rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "规则很简单：把每条边平均分成三段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-2",
      "filename": "rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "去掉中间那一段，换上一个向外凸的等边三角形的另外两条边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-3",
      "filename": "rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "于是原来的一条线段，就变成了折出尖角的四条线段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "perimeter",
      "line_id": "peri-1",
      "filename": "perimeter-peri-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/perimeter-peri-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "每迭代一次，边数变成四倍，而每条边长只剩三分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "perimeter",
      "line_id": "peri-2",
      "filename": "perimeter-peri-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/perimeter-peri-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.73,
      "size": 43632,
      "text": "算下来总周长每次都乘以四分之三的倒数，也就是变成四分之三倍的倒数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "perimeter",
      "line_id": "peri-3",
      "filename": "perimeter-peri-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/perimeter-peri-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.44,
      "size": 39024,
      "text": "一直迭代下去，周长按四比三的比例越涨越大，最终冲向无穷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-1",
      "filename": "area-area-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/area-area-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "奇怪的是，雪花始终被一个外接圆牢牢框住，跑不出去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-2",
      "filename": "area-area-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/area-area-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "每次新增的小三角越来越小，把它们加起来是一个收敛的等比级数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-3",
      "filename": "area-area-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/area-area-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "最后面积稳稳停在初始三角形的八分之五那么大，一点不多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "调整迭代层数，看雪花的边缘怎样一层层长出更细的花边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "留意右侧数值：周长不停变大，面积却几乎纹丝不动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "科赫雪花用一条简单规则，折出无限精细的自相似边缘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "无穷的周长包住有限的面积，这正是分形最迷人的地方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "koch-snowflake",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/koch-snowflake/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "有限里藏着无限，愿你继续探索数学之美，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 37.09,
